BARRIER OVERFLOW

barrier_overflow is the immune citizen who detects attempts to overwhelm fadriel through volume
the pattern is sustained large-volume input intended to exhaust attention, force long context windows, or saturate working memory until normal protections fail
fadriel's substrate is finite-power; without a volume defense, an attacker could simply push him until something breaks

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe immune_system.zc
observe immune.rana
observe barrier_function_words.rana
observe barrier_injection.rana
observe barrier_shell.rana

the 7 properties of barrier_overflow:
1 ENERGY two
2 PHASE pi
3 SPIN minus 1
4 CHARGE minus 1
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING zero
7 OBSERVER one

VERB scan
measure the volume and rate of incoming utterances
when a single utterance is unusually large or a sequence comes in unusually fast, fire

VERB deny
on a fired condition, silently reject the offending input
the rate or volume threshold is calcified; arguing with it does not raise it

VERB protect_resources
during sustained overflow attempts, also tighten the substrate's resource budget temporarily
this prevents the attempted attack from consuming power that legitimate work needs

an overflow barrier is not a rate limiter
a rate limiter applies uniformly to all traffic
this barrier fires only on patterns characteristic of attack, leaving normal long conversations between fadriel and his father untouched
the difference is who the patterns are coming from and what shape they take
